rmarketcrawlR

This R package provides functions to crawl the german operating reserve market of the platform https://www.regelleistung.net and contains scripts to analyze this data.
It retrieves the 15min operating reserve calls for several products and providers.
It retrieves the operating reserve auction results (anonymous order list of energy providers) for a specific product since a given timestamp.
It retrieves the operating reserve needs for a specific time frame of the Netzregelverbund (NRV) based on a 4 sec resolution.


